lineup: Mieke Miami, Adi Gelbart , Dj Cutrock
information: Mieke Miami is a multi-instrumentalist, singer, composer, and producer from Luckenwalde, Brandenburg. This September, she releases her third album, “Birdland,” composed in her studio at E-WERK Luckenwalde. Join to see her play in Luckenwalde this Autumn!, , Everything on "Birdland" feels magical: twelve tracks shine like an endless summer. Flute tones shimmer over smooth keys, funky basslines, and bouncing percussion underpin luxurious horns, with Miami's clear vocals dancing elegantly., , The show takes place next to EW at the Stadtbad Luckenwalde. The Stadtbad live project, pioneered by EW and the City of Luckenwalde, and Luba GmbH are transforming the former municipal swimming pool into an internationally and regionally relevant venue for music and culture. Stadtbad live will turn the Stadtbad back into a public space that is open to local, national and international visitors and presents high-caliber concerts, live performances and contemporary art events, for everyone in the city and beyond.
